    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "A rod of blackened bone with a bulb at one end comprises a *reaper's spellgun*, which feels heavier than it looks. You Activate the spellgun by aiming it at one creature and making your choice of a spell attack roll or a firearm attack roll against the target's AC. This spellgun has a range increment of 30 feet. The spellgun fires a shadowy ray, then dissolves into gray mist.",
